Class Plot

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Plot

  • public class Plot
extends java.lang.Object
    The Plot class keeps track of the plotId, ownerUsername timeCropPlanted, remainingPercentage, cropName and originalYield of a plot.
    Version:
    1.1 04 Apr 2020
    Author:
    Brian Goh
